The Matrix Revolutions is a 2003 American -- Australian science fiction action film written and directed by The Wachowski Brothers .
It was the third installment of the Matrix trilogy , released six months following The Matrix Reloaded .
The film was released simultaneously in 60 countries on November 5 , 2003 .
While it is the final film in the series , the Matrix storyline is continued in The Matrix Online .
It was the second live-action film to be released in both regular and IMAX theaters at the same time .
The film received generally average reviews from critics .